    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "All 7 assessed credibility factors meet their required gradation levels at MRL 2. The 6 not-assessed factors are appropriately scoped out per the MRL 2 requirements table. The CFD model demonstrates sufficient credibility to support the regulatory submission decision regarding worst-case hemolysis operating conditions for the Class II CPB device. The relative hemolysis index predictions are within 15% of experimental values across all operating points, and the RH < 1 acceptance criterion is satisfied with margin. The assessment team accepts the package for submission.",
